WEBVTT

00:07.800 --> 00:17.300
Modi must have told you very clearly about
how to grow in Sahaja Yog because he’s one

00:17.300 --> 00:26.010
of them who has really taken very positive
step to see that he grows.

00:26.010 --> 00:33.050
Now one has to understand one simple point
about realisation is that, just mere awakening

00:33.050 --> 00:39.370
of the Kundalini is not sufficient, that’s
just the beginning.

00:39.370 --> 00:48.559
You get your realisation but you must become
the tree, you have to grow, you have to become.

00:48.559 --> 00:57.020
If you cannot grow then you have not achieved
what you wanted to be.

00:57.020 --> 01:09.070
And you grow very fast, very fast with meditation
and with understanding about meditation.

01:09.070 --> 01:17.820
Now one of the few hurdles that we have, that
I’ve seen it, that are innately built in

01:17.820 --> 01:20.420
Sahaja Yog itself.

01:20.420 --> 01:25.810
One of them is that you get it spontaneously
so easily that you take it for granted.

01:25.810 --> 01:28.640
This is in the pattern of it, only innately
built.

01:28.640 --> 01:35.000
You see what ever you get so easily you just
take it for granted.

01:35.000 --> 01:41.110
But the another side of it is like that, that
when you have your eyes you don’t know the

01:41.110 --> 01:43.690
value of your eyes, you take it for granted.

01:43.690 --> 01:47.930
But when you don’t have them then you know
the value of eyes, it’s like that.

01:47.930 --> 01:55.200
So when you lose vibrations and when you get
out of Sahaja Yog, then you start feeling

01:55.200 --> 02:03.469
much more lost and then you come back to Sahaja
Yoga again.

02:03.469 --> 02:10.489
Like a person becomes rich, he enjoys the
riches and then you make him poor then he

02:10.489 --> 02:12.870
feels it more.

02:12.870 --> 02:14.340
So this is the correcting point.

02:14.340 --> 02:22.980
But it is very true that Sahaja has this thing
innately built in its self that it all happens

02:22.980 --> 02:30.349
very spontaneously and you get it for doing
nothing at all.

02:30.349 --> 02:41.709
So, may be so many of you may lose it because
you might find that it is just you got it

02:41.709 --> 02:42.709
because of something.

02:42.709 --> 02:48.140
I’ve also known of people they get vibrations
and they say, “Now it’s all right I don’t

02:48.140 --> 02:49.940
need Sahaja Yoga, I am on my own."

02:49.940 --> 02:56.099
Again they’re back like bad pennies with
some troubles and some problems and then they

02:56.099 --> 02:57.099
go out.

02:57.099 --> 03:03.931
Now I would say that Modi is one of those
first twelve people who got realisation, after

03:03.931 --> 03:09.129
two years I’ve worked on them, while you
got realisation in such a short time.

03:09.129 --> 03:16.470
Two years I’ve worked on twenty five people
out of which twelve got realisation you can

03:16.470 --> 03:21.690
imagine, two years! As I’ve told you in
London I’ve worked on six people for four

03:21.690 --> 03:26.769
years to give them realisation.

03:26.769 --> 03:34.540
But once a certain number of people of particular
ideologies of permutations and combinations,

03:34.540 --> 03:41.459
once they get realisation I find the rate
of realisation increases very fast.

03:41.459 --> 03:47.240
Like formally we never use to have anybody
in the program who has been to any other Guru,

03:47.240 --> 03:48.730
just avoid them.

03:48.730 --> 03:55.180
Even up to the point that this Modi himself
used to tell people there’s no program today,

03:55.180 --> 03:56.480
no program.

03:56.480 --> 03:59.890
And they would ring Me up and find out that
there was a program and why they were not

03:59.890 --> 04:00.890
allowed.

04:00.890 --> 04:02.330
They said “Mother we get headaches you see.

04:02.330 --> 04:06.930
They break our necks and they just disturb
us and they are good for nothing."

04:06.930 --> 04:12.830
But now, it’s very different, once we have
built up our strength of collectivity we have

04:12.830 --> 04:17.160
so many channels, things are working out very
differently.

04:17.160 --> 04:24.630
So the value that Modi would attach to his
realisation is much more than you would attach

04:24.630 --> 04:26.350
normally.

04:26.350 --> 04:36.380
Because as you see, first even say to have
a ordinary oil lamp was a problem.

04:36.380 --> 04:39.530
So the oil lamp was very important for people.

04:39.530 --> 04:44.450
They would see to it that they would not use
out all the oil and they were so careful.

04:44.450 --> 04:48.670
But today we have no problem, we have got
electricity we take it for granted.

04:48.670 --> 04:53.460
Only when the electricity goes off we know
what is electricity is.

04:53.460 --> 05:03.190
In the same way your realisation also, when
it is lost you understand the value of it.

05:03.190 --> 05:09.720
But supposing you have just touched it and
then you lose it, then you do not understand.

05:09.720 --> 05:15.260
But if you’ve got it you’ve enjoyed it
then you lose it then you want it back again,

05:15.260 --> 05:21.280
so best thing is to be steadily moving towards
your evolution.

05:21.280 --> 05:27.850
Now after I go away that’s the fears people
have here that people start doubting.

05:27.850 --> 05:31.120
They said, “It happened with people they
started doubting."

05:31.120 --> 05:33.090
Doubting what?

05:33.090 --> 05:37.680
Your doubting yourself is the main point is.

05:37.680 --> 05:41.470
You cannot believe that you can get realisation.

05:41.470 --> 05:44.210
This is the basic.

05:44.210 --> 05:53.240
You see to Me, it seems that you feel that
how can you get realisation?

05:53.240 --> 06:00.240
Only those who are very highly realised souls
know that you are realised, they know that

06:00.240 --> 06:04.630
you have been given realisation, but they
also sometimes ask Me, “Why did you give

06:04.630 --> 06:05.630
them realisation.

06:05.630 --> 06:12.910
What have they done?” Because you also think,
I mean we still have to look forward to something

06:12.910 --> 06:14.230
else.

06:14.230 --> 06:16.340
How can we get realisation, this is the trouble

06:16.340 --> 06:19.330
You don’t believe in yourself.

06:19.330 --> 06:24.370
That’s what you have to have confidence
in yourself and then you’ll have confidence

06:24.370 --> 06:27.060
in Me also.

06:27.060 --> 06:31.960
Because there are so many ways, by which you
can verify.

06:31.960 --> 06:33.000
First of all

06:33.000 --> 06:44.470
you can ask questions to the photograph or
to Me in your heart, about Myself, My relationship

06:44.470 --> 06:50.810
what ever you think could be, what ever you
think, put your imagination and see that what

06:50.810 --> 06:52.740
you think I could have been.

06:52.740 --> 06:54.260
Ask that question.

06:54.260 --> 06:57.300
Your vibrations will answer.

06:57.300 --> 07:03.980
Put your, stretch your imagination to the
last, what could be the last word you could

07:03.980 --> 07:05.540
think of Me.

07:05.540 --> 07:11.820
You see, some people will put doubts saying
that, “Kundalini awakening is very difficult,

07:11.820 --> 07:13.880
it is not easy."

07:13.880 --> 07:19.820
Yes it’s true, it’s not easy, it’s a
very difficult things for human beings.

07:19.820 --> 07:23.070
You just can’t do it, is a fact.

07:23.070 --> 07:32.130
You have to work for days with some guru in
some jungle all alone, seeing nobody, working

07:32.130 --> 07:35.960
out your chakras by chakras, sometimes you
have to starve, sometimes you have to eat,

07:35.960 --> 07:39.700
sometimes you have to breathe, you have to
do all kinds of things.

07:39.700 --> 07:41.090
And then the guru can work out.

07:41.090 --> 07:51.780
But there could be someone who is somehow
the master, could be someone.

07:51.780 --> 07:58.240
Kundalini is the Holy Ghost within you.

07:58.240 --> 08:06.000
So there could be someone like that who can
do the job and that is what it is.

08:06.000 --> 08:13.550
These things put you into doubts, because
you can’t believe it.

08:13.550 --> 08:16.240
In relation to yourself you can’t believe
it.

08:16.240 --> 08:20.420
You can believe in God, you can believe in
Holy Ghost, you can believe in Christ but

08:20.420 --> 08:27.300
you cannot believe that it has any relationship
with you, that you could be that great, that

08:27.300 --> 08:30.230
you could get your realisation.

08:30.230 --> 08:32.140
So just feel it and enjoy it.

08:32.140 --> 08:34.430
First of all, don’t think, that’s why
I say, “Don’t think."

08:34.430 --> 08:36.871
Because as soon as you start thinking, Mr.

08:36.871 --> 08:43.159
Thomas in you will get up and say that “Hello,
this cannot be Self-realisation."

08:43.159 --> 08:44.159
Mr.

08:44.159 --> 08:46.180
Thomas was great, you see.

08:46.180 --> 08:52.830
Christ had all the disciples and I find all
those types around, permutations and combinations

08:52.830 --> 08:56.820
and some how Judas also, but they’re rarely
to be found.

08:56.820 --> 09:05.240
But there are, no doubt and some are Thomas’s,
and these Thomas’ are described as murmuring

09:05.240 --> 09:06.890
souls by Christ Himself.

09:06.890 --> 09:11.640
He said, “These are murmuring souls,”
and they murmur and one murmuring soul comes

09:11.640 --> 09:16.880
to you, another murmuring soul in you joins
hands and you start all murmuring together,

09:16.880 --> 09:17.880
start thinking.

09:17.880 --> 09:22.560
Now at that time what have you to do on rational
grounds is very simple.

09:22.560 --> 09:25.140
What have I done so far?

09:25.140 --> 09:31.970
I’ve done everything, did I get cool breeze?

09:31.970 --> 09:35.830
Did I get my self realisation?

09:35.830 --> 09:40.210
Did I feel my own powers?

09:40.210 --> 09:43.210
Have I been able to feel myself and others?

09:43.210 --> 09:49.900
Because you see your still not fully realised,
you may not be able to feel the vibrations

09:49.900 --> 09:54.680
of another person, neither you will be able
to feel your own vibrations.

09:54.680 --> 10:01.520
But there are so many people here who are
realised and they can feel yours, and they

10:01.520 --> 10:02.600
can verify.

10:02.600 --> 10:08.930
Supposing they ask you, “How is your father?”

10:08.930 --> 10:12.300
There was one gentleman in England he came
and told Me, “Why is everybody asking me

10:12.300 --> 10:13.300
about my father?”

10:13.300 --> 10:17.750
I said, “Because there’s one particular
centre that’s catching,” and I called

10:17.750 --> 10:22.030
a child I said now tell Me, “What is the
centre catching?” She pointed out this one

10:22.030 --> 10:23.900
and I said, “This is the centre."

10:23.900 --> 10:27.070
Everybody is catching on this centre, this
is the father centre so they’re asking you

10:27.070 --> 10:28.180
about your father.

10:28.180 --> 10:32.330
He said, “Yes he’s dead and he died of
cancer and he had this and that,” and we

10:32.330 --> 10:33.770
had to treat him.

10:33.770 --> 10:39.930
For example anorexia is a disease can be cured
by curing this centre.

10:39.930 --> 10:47.900
It’s such a deep knowledge and it is such
an all pervading knowledge.

10:47.900 --> 10:56.310
Because once you know in a tree the sap that
goes to all the leaves and all the ends of

10:56.310 --> 11:01.361
it and if you can move the sap, your attention
can move with the sap, you can know the whole

11:01.361 --> 11:03.850
of the tree.

11:03.850 --> 11:08.950
You cannot know leaves and then know the tree.

11:08.950 --> 11:10.990
How many leaves can you count?

11:10.990 --> 11:16.130
But to know the tree the best thing is to
get to the sap.

11:16.130 --> 11:20.550
To treat a tree is best is to get to its sap,
isn’t it?

11:20.550 --> 11:30.830
In the same way when you go from inside out
then you find that you know yourself and others

11:30.830 --> 11:31.830
very well.

11:31.830 --> 11:35.740
It’s very simple even small children can
do it.

11:35.740 --> 11:42.000
So the first doubt comes about yourself, “Oh
this is one of them” because there’s a

11:42.000 --> 11:43.490
guru shopping going on, you see.

11:43.490 --> 11:50.769
There’s a guru shopping, there’s a float,
you go to one guru to another, to ESPs and

11:50.769 --> 11:58.150
what you call them, all sorts of things, mediums,
and all sorts of things they do with the dead

11:58.150 --> 11:59.740
bodies or anything.

11:59.740 --> 12:03.700
All these things you have been to and you
will have found it.

12:03.700 --> 12:09.720
So now suddenly you have to come to a temple,
where you don’t pay anything and you just

12:09.720 --> 12:10.720
get the blessings.

12:10.720 --> 12:16.420
So can’t believe it, you just can’t believe
it, it’s too much to believe.

12:16.420 --> 12:18.120
This is what happens you get

12:18.120 --> 12:19.120
confused.

12:19.120 --> 12:25.220
You are all ready confused, but confusion
could be over by understanding that something

12:25.220 --> 12:29.890
is happening to you just wait and see, give
it a chance.

12:29.890 --> 12:37.760
There’s no way we can bind you to Sahaja
Yoga, because there’s no mesmerism here.

12:37.760 --> 12:41.350
This is another innately a problem with Sahaja
Yoga.

12:41.350 --> 12:47.490
Second problem I should say is that you’re
too free to do what you like, absolutely free,

12:47.490 --> 12:55.690
there’s no binding force except that you
feel the love of your Mother.

12:55.690 --> 12:59.690
Supposing you are not feeling the vibrations
in your hand, there’s no way of binding

12:59.690 --> 13:01.840
you down to Sahaja Yog, nothing.

13:01.840 --> 13:06.960
We just advise “Go ahead, it will work out,
let it work out."

13:06.960 --> 13:11.810
There is no fees, there’s no registration,
there’s no compulsion, nothing.

13:11.810 --> 13:14.200
It’s your own free will.

13:14.200 --> 13:19.740
If you want to stick on you can stick on,
if you want to go away you can go away.

13:19.740 --> 13:22.880
There’s no force on you of any kind.

13:22.880 --> 13:28.540
There’s no registration of your names with
some fees or anything, I mean you are not

13:28.540 --> 13:31.240
bound to pay anything.

13:31.240 --> 13:34.211
If you paid something then you feel, “All
right I’ve paid for it, so go through it

13:34.211 --> 13:35.800
what ever it is, good or bad..

13:35.800 --> 13:39.960
Supposing you go to see a play and it’s
a horrid play but still you say, “All right

13:39.960 --> 13:42.570
I’ve paid for it so let me go through it."

13:42.570 --> 13:48.290
But that you cannot do with Sahaja Yog because
you’ve not paid.

13:48.290 --> 13:52.920
There’s nobody will force you down, nobody
will go on telephoning to you, “Come along,

13:52.920 --> 13:54.630
please come along,” and all that.

13:54.630 --> 13:58.029
So the attitude has to be changed, it is I
who has to gain.

13:58.029 --> 14:01.920
Say there’s a beautiful spot somewhere.

14:01.920 --> 14:07.279
Now that beautiful spot doesn’t send an
invitation card to anyone, everybody goes

14:07.279 --> 14:08.279
there.

14:08.279 --> 14:12.190
But if you have not yet discovered the beauty
of Sahaja Yog in that way and have not enjoyed

14:12.190 --> 14:15.541
it fully, you’ll have to go again and again
and see for yourself.

14:15.541 --> 14:23.670
It is a deliberation on your side not on the
side of the Sahaja Yogis or Sahaja Yoga.

14:23.670 --> 14:26.500
It’s not going to fall at your feet.

14:26.500 --> 14:32.410
That please come to Sahaja Yoga, please donate
something, nothing of the kind.

14:32.410 --> 14:38.970
If you come you are welcome, if you don’t
come, welcome.

14:38.970 --> 14:44.500
On the contrary, you will be surprised there’s
more rejection than acceptance in Sahaja Yog.

14:44.500 --> 14:46.060
That’s also innately built.

14:46.060 --> 14:50.021
I’ve seen some people who are very insincere
type they just go out from Sahaja Yoga like

14:50.021 --> 14:51.650
a tangent.

14:51.650 --> 14:57.300
There was a gentleman who was very troublesome
to us in Bombay and we didn’t know what

14:57.300 --> 15:06.170
to do with him and he just got transferred
from there and we got rid of him.

15:06.170 --> 15:14.650
So you just go out of Sahaja Yoga like a tangent
and we are saved from the botheration.

15:14.650 --> 15:19.660
Because you must understand, if you have problems,
if you are not all right it’s a problem

15:19.660 --> 15:21.520
for Sahaja Yogis to correct you.

15:21.520 --> 15:27.910
It’s just the other way round, if you understand
this, then you will understand the thing,

15:27.910 --> 15:28.910
what works out.

15:28.910 --> 15:33.700
For example if I have to cure somebody it’s
a problem for Me and not the problem for the

15:33.700 --> 15:35.910
person who’s sick.

15:35.910 --> 15:43.290
Now if the tree has to grow is the problem
for the gardener not for the tree.

15:43.290 --> 15:52.110
So the tree must see to it that it co-operates
with the gardener and gets itself developed.

15:52.110 --> 15:58.170
If this understanding is developed, that it
is I who has to gain, it is I who has to go

15:58.170 --> 16:06.190
forward, Mother has not to gain from me anything,
She wants me to have all my powers manifested.

16:06.190 --> 16:13.740
She wants me to grow through it, if this attitude
is developed then you’ll work hard to grow

16:13.740 --> 16:15.980
and you’ll work it out.

16:15.980 --> 16:21.710
But on the contrary you see at the slightest
protest if you ego stands up and says, “Why,

16:21.710 --> 16:25.980
why should I do this?”

16:25.980 --> 16:31.810
To overcome this hurdle you see, we have to
build up certain stages.

16:31.810 --> 16:35.970
That’s what Modi was telling Me.

16:35.970 --> 16:40.110
That you first become thoughtlessly aware,
see that silence is established.

16:40.110 --> 16:47.020
There are certain things that you do much
later, everybody is not allowed in there,

16:47.020 --> 16:54.470
because truth can be only born by people who
are strong enough to bear it.

16:54.470 --> 17:03.900
That’s why I’m not going to tell you who
am I, till you reach a certain stage, because

17:03.900 --> 17:05.470
you cannot bear the light.

17:05.470 --> 17:08.100
That’s what happened with Christ.

17:08.100 --> 17:12.440
They crucified Him because they could not
bear Him.

17:12.440 --> 17:19.319
Human beings are like that, they can’t even
bear an incarnation of love.

17:19.319 --> 17:23.260
They can’t even bear love, it’s too much
for them.

17:23.260 --> 17:29.190
Even if you give them too much love they get
upset, they get disturbed, they just can’t

17:29.190 --> 17:30.190
bear it.

17:30.190 --> 17:34.781
So you have to build up yourself to come to
a certain stage of understanding of Sahaja

17:34.781 --> 17:35.781
Yoga.

17:35.781 --> 17:37.450
It’s a state, which you achieve.

17:37.450 --> 17:39.410
It’s a state.

17:39.410 --> 17:45.660
You are not to be certified by anyone on the...But
it’s a state where you will start giving

17:45.660 --> 17:52.179
realisation to others and the whole way you’ll
be talking you will be in a very different

17:52.179 --> 17:54.620
manner as if you are completely detached.

17:54.620 --> 17:58.280
You’ll say “It is going, it is coming."

17:58.280 --> 17:59.280
It happens.

17:59.280 --> 18:04.250
You will not say my mother must get, my father
must get, you will never say like that.

18:04.250 --> 18:11.630
Because you’ll understand that the problem
of Sahaja Yoga is that it cannot give to anyone.

18:11.630 --> 18:12.840
Like

18:12.840 --> 18:20.350
the sunshine can shine it is for the trees
to expose themselves to the sunshine and get

18:20.350 --> 18:22.850
the advantage of it.

18:22.850 --> 18:29.240
The sunshine is not going to run after you
all over to see that you get it.

18:29.240 --> 18:38.030
This is the point here, it will shine the
whole day and you take it.

18:38.030 --> 18:42.890
But it’s not that it will run after you
all the time requesting you, “Oh please

18:42.890 --> 18:47.990
get me, oh please get me, have it, have it,”
like that.

18:47.990 --> 18:57.470
And this is what one has to understand very
clearly, that it is you who has to ask for

18:57.470 --> 19:02.390
it, and not anybody is going to force on you
anything.

19:02.390 --> 19:09.360
On the contrary if anybody tries to say something
more your ego gets like that.

19:09.360 --> 19:11.830
So try to be careful.

19:11.830 --> 19:17.970
I am very happy to know that also, that in
all the ego orientated societies I’ve seen

19:17.970 --> 19:20.470
that Sahaja Yoga works like wonders.

19:20.470 --> 19:23.640
Because first thing they see is their colossal
ego.

19:23.640 --> 19:28.140
And that’s a very positive point about it,
because once you start seeing this horrible

19:28.140 --> 19:34.750
balloon in you, you just start watching yourself
and enjoying, “Oh Mr so and now get along

19:34.750 --> 19:35.750
with your ego."

19:35.750 --> 19:38.610
You see it’s a very interesting life you
start leading.

19:38.610 --> 19:44.990
If your ego you see, is a very good sign.

19:44.990 --> 19:48.250
If you cannot see your ego then there’s
danger.

19:48.250 --> 19:51.809
But some can even see their super ego if they’re
possessed.

19:51.809 --> 19:58.030
See people see how they get possessed suddenly
because the frequency of possession becomes

19:58.030 --> 20:06.360
very little so that there’s a big gaps you
see to see the time when you are normal and

20:06.360 --> 20:11.400
when you get abnormal also you can see clearly
that you are abnormal.

20:11.400 --> 20:18.020
By seeing that you start judging, “Oh God
I have again been caught up, I’m again lost,”

20:18.020 --> 20:19.910
and you come back to normal.

20:19.910 --> 20:29.400
The whole thing becomes a very beautiful understanding
of the reality about yourself and you laugh

20:29.400 --> 20:31.520
at yourself all the time.

20:31.520 --> 20:36.250
All the time you laugh at your self and you
laugh at everything and you find the whole

20:36.250 --> 20:41.650
joke going round how people are seriously
indulging into nonsensical things and how

20:41.650 --> 20:48.060
it’s such a big joke you’ve been yourself
worrying about things which have no meaning,

20:48.060 --> 20:50.150
which has no significance.

20:50.150 --> 20:55.600
Like I went first to Paris and people told
Me, “Mother they are not going to like you

20:55.600 --> 21:01.510
very much, because they believe a person who
is so happy is ignorant.

21:01.510 --> 21:02.950
You should not be a happy person.

21:02.950 --> 21:06.299
You should be a crying baby so they’ll believe
You."

21:06.299 --> 21:11.320
They’re all les miserable, very unhappy
people, extremely unhappy and if you tell

21:11.320 --> 21:16.020
them you are a happy person so they are going
to be shocked at such a thing.

21:16.020 --> 21:20.150
I said, “Really this Les Miserable, let
me (inaudible).

21:20.150 --> 21:25.840
Let Me do something about them and I made
them laugh so much at their miseries that

21:25.840 --> 21:30.179
they got all right and they understood that
the joy is just there.

21:30.179 --> 21:35.670
You have to just peep in your heart and you’ll
find the source of your joy and then the whole

21:35.670 --> 21:37.330
thing vanishes into thin air.

21:37.330 --> 21:40.820
But it has to work, it has to happen.

21:40.820 --> 21:48.890
There is no quick way of doing it in the sense
that I say, “All right you give me five

21:48.890 --> 21:52.480
rupees or five dollars, Australian dollars
and you get it."

21:52.480 --> 21:56.910
NO, no, no, no, you may give Me any amount
it won’t work out.

21:56.910 --> 22:00.370
It has not worked out with My own daughters
you’ll be surprised.

22:00.370 --> 22:02.970
I’ve never forced them or I’ve never asked
them.

22:02.970 --> 22:06.370
I’ve only two daughters they’re not realised
I’m not bothered.

22:06.370 --> 22:09.230
When they’ll ask for it they’ll get it.

22:09.230 --> 22:11.390
But My four grandchildren are born realised.

22:11.390 --> 22:17.090
And one of the eldest ones one day very seriously
said, “As it is you cannot commit mistakes

22:17.090 --> 22:24.830
I know but it would have been nice if you
have given them realisation when they were

22:24.830 --> 22:25.830
children."

22:25.830 --> 22:31.880
You see this is what it is that you cannot
force these things on anyone and you have

22:31.880 --> 22:34.720
to take a very detached view.

22:34.720 --> 22:40.140
You are a seeker, your mother and you are
there but they are not your responsibility,

22:40.140 --> 22:41.950
you can tell them about Sahaja Yog.

22:41.950 --> 22:45.929
But if they are opposing you better have,
let them be alone, they’ll come round.

22:45.929 --> 22:51.000
When they see the transformation in within
you, they’ll definitely come.

22:51.000 --> 22:52.730
So leave them alone.

22:52.730 --> 22:54.870
Don’t bother your heads.

22:54.870 --> 23:01.190
Just leave them alone and you will be amazed
that they will see you transforming so well

23:01.190 --> 23:07.390
and acting so well and they’ll change themselves
and they will come to you and ask you, “How

23:07.390 --> 23:14.820
are you so much changed and transformed?”
You see proof of the pudding is in seeing

23:14.820 --> 23:19.780
the pudding up there changing people.

23:19.780 --> 23:26.740
And this transformation you’ll be amazed
coming into you so suddenly that you will

23:26.740 --> 23:29.310
be amazed.

23:29.310 --> 23:36.440
But as I told you that on the left side is
the desire or you can say the super ego, the

23:36.440 --> 23:38.100
desire to do something.

23:38.100 --> 23:46.390
And the right side is the ego which we try
to sort of please and which feels happy and

23:46.390 --> 23:48.120
the one by which we have ambitions.

23:48.120 --> 23:52.309
But in the centre is the will power to do
this.

23:52.309 --> 23:58.100
And this will power has to be increased by
you, “I have to do it, I have to do it."

23:58.100 --> 23:59.500
First you’ll feel tired because

23:59.500 --> 24:03.190
your left heart is weak, then I will tell
you how to do it.

24:03.190 --> 24:06.610
‘Then know how to raise your left heart
if you’re tired.

24:06.610 --> 24:12.410
See most of the people these days are very
tired people.

24:12.410 --> 24:14.630
They talk, “Ah,” they sit down “Ah."

24:14.630 --> 24:18.940
They can’t, I mean they are very tired,
absolutely fagged out people.

24:18.940 --> 24:21.640
Morning till evening what have you been doing,
nothing.

24:21.640 --> 24:27.640
Just sitting in the sun you got tired, just
lazing out you got tired.

24:27.640 --> 24:29.790
Why, why did you get tired?

24:29.790 --> 24:34.850
Firstly because you’re not integrated you
are fighting with in yourself.

24:34.850 --> 24:39.850
You’re head is fighting your heart, your
heart is fighting your liver.

24:39.850 --> 24:44.010
Secondly, you are thinking and wasting your
energy.

24:44.010 --> 24:52.640
So you have to learn how to settle your heart,
what has to be done to raise your heart to

24:52.640 --> 24:58.120
make it peaceful and how to get the energy
from your spirit.

24:58.120 --> 25:02.560
Once you start doing that your tired feeling
will go away.

25:02.560 --> 25:08.640
Then your aggressiveness also will decrease
and you’ll be amazed that you will just

25:08.640 --> 25:09.919
watch the whole thing.

25:09.919 --> 25:16.590
Neither you’ll aggress nor you’ll take
aggression and the whole reaction will be

25:16.590 --> 25:18.010
very different.

25:18.010 --> 25:23.120
Then everything has a meaning, your feelings
have a meaning.

25:23.120 --> 25:28.780
Supposing you have a feeling today for Poland,
which is in trouble, all of you should ask

25:28.780 --> 25:31.700
just now, “Mother solve the problem of Poland."

25:31.700 --> 25:36.990
Because I have no desires you see, I am desire
less, you have to ask and it works, you’ll

25:36.990 --> 25:41.580
be amazed because your attention is enlightened
now, it just works.

25:41.580 --> 25:44.010
You have to desire for it and it works.

25:44.010 --> 25:45.010
You have to work for it and it works.

25:45.010 --> 25:51.840
And so many miraculous things people will
tell you just believe them that’s all true.

25:51.840 --> 25:59.400
Money problem solved, because of Lakshmi Tattwa
within, financial problems solved, social

25:59.400 --> 26:04.850
problem solved, family problems solved because
you are solved.

26:04.850 --> 26:07.860
See in relation to you all everything seems
problematic.

26:07.860 --> 26:12.179
When your problems are solved everything is
solved.

26:12.179 --> 26:14.620
It’s so simple as that.

26:14.620 --> 26:19.780
We have to solve ourselves and it is solved
through the awakening of the Kundalini.

26:19.780 --> 26:24.900
Now I would like to have some questions from
you and then I would like you to go into groups

26:24.900 --> 26:31.929
with the Sahaja Yogis and talk to them on
intimate level and also you must tell Me your

26:31.929 --> 26:32.929
problems.

26:32.929 --> 26:35.679
If you have any intimate problems, you can
talk to Me also.

26:35.679 --> 26:42.610
But best is to talk to each other.
I would like Warren to see to it that he organises

26:42.610 --> 26:44.549
all these groups properly.

26:44.549 --> 26:58.220
But I would love to have some questions from
you about Sahaja Yoga now.

26:58.220 --> 27:03.310
Question: How can one laugh at abortion.

27:03.310 --> 27:09.760
He's talking about abortion, you are taking
the view that it is bad?

27:09.760 --> 27:17.240
Shri Mataji: I’m not saying you have to,
I said you are not to laugh, means you laugh

27:17.240 --> 27:20.530
at silly stupid things I meant, you see.

27:20.530 --> 27:26.000
But at abortion as I can’t understand you
see.

27:26.000 --> 27:28.340
This is a very funny situation in this country.

27:28.340 --> 27:31.520
As it is the birth rate is minus and you are
having abortions.

27:31.520 --> 27:35.120
Question: Does it exist in India much abortion

27:35.120 --> 27:38.510
Shri Mataji: Not much, people don’t like
it at all, they hate it.

27:38.510 --> 27:41.650
And you know the trouble is like this.

27:41.650 --> 27:45.650
You people are having no children so we have
to have the load on us.

27:45.650 --> 27:47.900
You see what to do?

27:47.900 --> 27:52.260
Nobody to be born here, they don’t want
to be born here because there is no love in

27:52.260 --> 27:53.950
the heart.

27:53.950 --> 27:58.059
See when the other day when somebody told
Me about the doctors here some of them are

27:58.059 --> 28:00.710
butchers I couldn’t believe it.

28:00.710 --> 28:03.980
Because in India at least, doctors are not
butchers by any chance.

28:03.980 --> 28:08.730
I was surprised; this is because everything
has become a butchery here, because the heart

28:08.730 --> 28:10.760
is covered with ego.

28:10.760 --> 28:13.330
There’s no heart left.

28:13.330 --> 28:14.950
You have to raise the heart.

28:14.950 --> 28:21.130
That’s important, once you raise the heart,
you see you cannot stand all this nonsense,

28:21.130 --> 28:22.130
you know.

28:22.130 --> 28:24.160
Why do you want to have abortion I still can’t
understand?

28:24.160 --> 28:26.900
Question: Does it affect Swadisthan charka?

28:26.900 --> 28:31.210
Shri Mataji: Oh, it affects many chakras,
I mean.

28:31.210 --> 28:37.880
There was someone I knew who always used to
catch on right heart, I must tell you this,

28:37.880 --> 28:40.130
very nice person, always on right heart.

28:40.130 --> 28:47.400
His father was a good man everything was fine,
asked him, “How are you catching on right

28:47.400 --> 28:53.160
heart?” He was not married and when he came
very close to Me then he confessed to Me that,

28:53.160 --> 29:00.610
“I lived with a woman and she was going
to have a baby and she went in for an abortion

29:00.610 --> 29:04.910
and I conceded, and since then

29:04.910 --> 29:09.669
I have been feeling very sad about the whole
thing."

29:09.669 --> 29:16.679
But the whole view about life has to be changed
then only you can avoid these things.

29:16.679 --> 29:19.309
You see it is a symptom of a disease.

29:19.309 --> 29:25.419
It’s not the disease itself, abortion is
not the disease, is a symptom of a disease.

29:25.419 --> 29:32.560
Now what is the disease with in us is, is
that, that we have allowed our sex to be let

29:32.560 --> 29:36.120
loose completely, talking too much about sex
from childhood.

29:36.120 --> 29:39.710
What is the need to give education in sex,
I’ve been failed to understand?

29:39.710 --> 29:45.360
Openly, there’s no need to teach about,
you see, do the animals need any sex education,

29:45.360 --> 29:47.480
they still produce.

29:47.480 --> 29:55.320
Then they told Me, “They tell about sex
only because they think by telling about sex

29:55.320 --> 29:58.179
they can protect people from not going into
sex."

29:58.179 --> 30:02.110
I said, “No, they create too much of curiosity
in children."

30:02.110 --> 30:07.620
For example, in India we never talk about
sex to children, they do not know, they are

30:07.620 --> 30:08.620
so innocent.

30:08.620 --> 30:14.250
Even till the marriage takes place some of
the girls do not know what sex actually is,

30:14.250 --> 30:15.780
how it works out and all.

30:15.780 --> 30:21.370
But they are told this is something filthy
to do and all that and when the girl gets

30:21.370 --> 30:27.210
into puberty it is told and to the boys also,
somehow or other it is a very different society.

30:27.210 --> 30:30.940
This question doesn’t come, it never comes
into the head of the boys and girls.

30:30.940 --> 30:36.690
You see if you keep them pure, like it doesn’t
come in the head of a sister and a brother

30:36.690 --> 30:39.929
even today, thank God.

30:39.929 --> 30:44.440
Many sisters and brothers I should say despite
Freud’s all efforts to spoil your minds,

30:44.440 --> 30:46.900
but still there are brothers and sisters relations
today.

30:46.900 --> 30:53.480
In the same way it doesn’t come into their
heads at all.

30:53.480 --> 30:58.410
And when they get married they are to be told,
this is what it is.

30:58.410 --> 31:03.100
And that’s why they say these koarak and
all these places were built where they could

31:03.100 --> 31:07.650
take young brides and young people to see
that.

31:07.650 --> 31:14.090
This was called as Koomari Kar Temple, means
the married women when they were not virgins

31:14.090 --> 31:21.020
could go there and see those places to understand
what is sex is and they got so exhausted with

31:21.020 --> 31:25.450
this early sex life, I mean you go into all
kinds of tantrums then.

31:25.450 --> 31:28.540
Because you’re so exhausted then you go
into perversions.

31:28.540 --> 31:30.159
The basics are wrong.

31:30.159 --> 31:33.770
We are trying too hard to be sexologists.

31:33.770 --> 31:39.360
There’s no need to be sex points you are
that already.

31:39.360 --> 31:44.679
But you don’t want to be only sex points,
do you?

31:44.679 --> 31:55.321
I don’t know what makes you feel that that
is the end of every, every endeavor, everything

31:55.321 --> 31:56.500
should end up there.

31:56.500 --> 32:01.559
May be that advertisement and all this is
coming to you too much because they think

32:01.559 --> 32:04.150
that by exploiting these things they will
help you.

32:04.150 --> 32:18.580
But it’s such a perverted thing and

32:18.580 --> 32:33.600
Seeker interrupts and asks Shri Mataji about
people in India being given a gift like a

32:33.600 --> 32:35.360
transistor radio for sterilization.

32:35.360 --> 32:38.660
Does it have a purpose?

32:38.660 --> 32:47.830
It has a purpose to a point.....Oh I'm sorry
this has another point....

32:47.830 --> 32:52.610
He is talking about in India where they give
a transistor radio....

32:52.610 --> 33:00.299
Shri Mataji: That’s what they try, this
is also, you see western ideas coming to India.

33:00.299 --> 33:03.720
Oh, they did all sorts just to sterilise them.

33:03.720 --> 33:08.110
Oh! that’s how the lady lost her last election,
last election she has now pulled her ears

33:08.110 --> 33:09.110
for that.

33:09.110 --> 33:13.640
You see, they are all westernised people you
see, they try to try all these tricks in....

33:13.640 --> 33:15.340
People don’t like it you see.

33:15.340 --> 33:28.450
There’s a bridegroom who went for his wedding
and poor thing saw that there was a team of

33:28.450 --> 33:30.169
people standing there for sterilisation.

33:30.169 --> 33:38.270
He jumped out of the bus and he disappeared
forever, nobody knows where he is, disappeared.

33:38.270 --> 33:44.630
‘And they even sterilised people who were
very old and who were not even married you

33:44.630 --> 33:45.630
see.

33:45.630 --> 33:50.040
It’s so funny, so indiscriminate, I think
they were possessed by some bhoots I don’t

33:50.040 --> 33:51.400
know what to call them.

33:51.400 --> 33:59.810
You see population is a problem in India but
what to do now, you should solve the problem.

33:59.810 --> 34:03.650
And there is something working out in a very
funny way, I must tell you.

34:03.650 --> 34:08.950
I went to Colombia, I found lots of these
Norwegians carrying Colombian children with

34:08.950 --> 34:09.950
them.

34:09.950 --> 34:14.409
And they looked so different from Norwegian
children, Norwegian people and these Colombian

34:14.409 --> 34:15.409
children.

34:15.409 --> 34:18.669
I asked them, “Why do you acquire these
children where are you carrying them?

34:18.669 --> 34:23.889
They said “We have adopted them”.
I said, “Why don’t you produce your own?

34:23.889 --> 34:25.710
That would be better, to produce your own."

34:25.710 --> 34:32.540
"No we don’t want to go through the process
of it, it’s better to have ready made."

34:32.540 --> 34:38.960
So the supply has started in having all this
in developing countries to give you ready

34:38.960 --> 34:39.960
made children.

34:39.960 --> 34:45.289
Isn’t if funny, it’s funny things going
on, instant babies.

34:45.289 --> 34:55.869
Question: If a chakra is blocked and you clean
the chakras wouldn’t you being undoing the

34:55.869 --> 35:02.099
karmic cycle that a person has to go through?

35:02.099 --> 35:08.211
Shri Mataji: Very good idea, Because I think
you people...I know the question is this,

35:08.211 --> 35:13.729
that he is saying that if you try to clean
the chakras you will be undoing the karmic

35:13.729 --> 35:20.759
cycle and all that you see this is the typical
things that are being circulated in the west

35:20.759 --> 35:21.779
you see.

35:21.779 --> 35:26.890
That you have your own karmas you see and
we are the gurus so you have to go through

35:26.890 --> 35:30.930
your karmas, you must suffer for your karmas
you see like that is there.

35:30.930 --> 35:37.420
Now, this theory was all right before Christ
came in, not after His coming.

35:37.420 --> 35:39.749
And why are they here then?

35:39.749 --> 35:42.469
Why are we paying them, for what?

35:42.469 --> 35:44.299
You better pickle them out.

35:44.299 --> 35:49.200
They’re worth nothing because they just
take money from you, and we have to go through

35:49.200 --> 35:50.200
our karmas.

35:50.200 --> 35:53.200
They make you dance, jump go into all kinds
of things.

35:53.200 --> 35:56.279
Put spirits in us and say, “You are suffering
your karmas.

35:56.279 --> 36:02.640
Why should we suffer?” At least they should
suffer for our karma’s minimum of minimum.

36:02.640 --> 36:04.769
Now Christ has done that for you.

36:04.769 --> 36:09.170
He has taken all these karmas, your karmas
upon Himself.

36:09.170 --> 36:15.249
He has made way for us, that’s why you have
to pass through Him.

36:15.249 --> 36:22.890
Once you pass through Him, through Agnya chakra,
your karmas are sucked in by Him, that’s

36:22.890 --> 36:24.289
your ego.

36:24.289 --> 36:29.099
It’s the only ego that says you have done
this wrong, and that wrong.

36:29.099 --> 36:33.829
You see an animal doesn’t think that way.

36:33.829 --> 36:37.509
It thinks it’s it own sva bhavah the way
it has to be.

36:37.509 --> 36:42.130
But it’s only the human beings who think
I’ve done this wrong, I’ve done that wrong.

36:42.130 --> 36:45.250
I’ve done this good, that bad because we
have ego.

36:45.250 --> 36:55.190
But when your Kundalini passes through your
Agnya chakra your ego is sucked in, your superego

36:55.190 --> 36:56.190
is sucked in.

36:56.190 --> 37:00.849
Christ has done double job in one shot you
know, it’s great.

37:00.849 --> 37:08.170
That’s why He was crucified, it was to be.

37:08.170 --> 37:15.910
He took all your karmas upon Himself and put
it into hell.

37:15.910 --> 37:22.969
So what ever karmas you have done are all
sucked in.

37:22.969 --> 37:25.210
But the door must open fully.

37:25.210 --> 37:30.529
In the beginning it happens that only a thread
comes up, you see, and the ego is not fully

37:30.529 --> 37:34.640
sucked in so sometimes it still comes up and
all that.

37:34.640 --> 37:39.480
The best weapon to get rid of them is to forgive
others.

37:39.480 --> 37:46.299
Forgiveness is the greatest weapon Christ
has given us, which we have to use, forgive,

37:46.299 --> 37:48.220
forgive and forgive.

37:48.220 --> 37:57.319
That’s a very good way, Lords Prayer is
the solution for your Agnya charka, you’ll

37:57.319 --> 37:58.400
be amazed.

37:58.400 --> 38:03.960
You have to say Lords Prayer after realisation
to open your Agnya.

38:03.960 --> 38:06.170
Then you become thoughtlessly aware.

38:06.170 --> 38:10.630
After realisation again I say, not before
realisation, it has no meaning.

38:10.630 --> 38:14.619
Before realisation what ever you have said
has gone into karmas.

38:14.619 --> 38:21.869
Only after realisation you are baptized and
get an opening here and all your karmas pass

38:21.869 --> 38:25.289
through that.

38:25.289 --> 38:29.469
Also you will find when you get realisation
lot of heat comes out these are the karmas

38:29.469 --> 38:32.890
you see, that are coming out.

38:32.890 --> 38:36.730
Let the heat go out and all karmas are finished.

38:36.730 --> 38:38.430
It’s like that.

38:38.430 --> 38:41.529
This is what is Self-Realisation.

38:41.529 --> 38:51.190
Like an egg is in a egg shell is very different,
but when it becomes a little chick and the

38:51.190 --> 39:01.239
mother breaks the tip of the egg a new bird
comes out with out any karmas or the smell

39:01.239 --> 39:03.489
of the egg.

39:03.489 --> 39:08.710
So clean and nice, every thing converted into
something beautiful.

39:08.710 --> 39:14.930
It’s like that, this is the rebirth.

39:14.930 --> 39:19.950
This is how we become a new personality a
new being.

39:19.950 --> 39:22.993
So to forget about your karmas after your
realisation, all right.

39:22.993 --> 39:25.849
He has said it

39:25.849 --> 39:31.489
that, “He died for your sins."

39:31.489 --> 39:34.440
Didn’t He?

39:34.440 --> 39:37.569
And the wages of sin is fear.

39:37.569 --> 39:42.420
If you still have fear within you of your
karmas, you are still sinning.

39:42.420 --> 39:46.349
There should be no fear about it.

39:46.349 --> 39:52.039
Do not have any guilt, I’ve been telling
you not to have any guilt.

39:52.039 --> 39:55.010
What can you do?

39:55.010 --> 39:56.010
What sins can you commit?

39:56.010 --> 39:59.940
Do not have any fears.

39:59.940 --> 40:05.380
This is very common as I told you the other
day left Vishuddhi, I have to talk about it

40:05.380 --> 40:06.380
quite a lot.

40:06.380 --> 40:11.710
It’s so common, in Australia, in America
and in all the western countries, to feel

40:11.710 --> 40:12.710
guilty.

40:12.710 --> 40:17.200
Everything collapses there and nobody can
rise through the Agnya because it collapses

40:17.200 --> 40:20.420
down here onto left Vishuddhi where you feel
guilty.

40:20.420 --> 40:22.440
What are you feeling guilty about?

40:22.440 --> 40:24.430
And why did Christ come on this earth.

40:24.430 --> 40:26.960
You are just wasting His incarnation by feeling
guilty yourself.

40:26.960 --> 40:31.599
He has taken all your guilt upon Himself.

40:31.599 --> 40:34.869
What do you thing He was?

40:34.869 --> 40:42.589
He was Omkara, he was Pranava, He was the
word, He was that power.

40:42.589 --> 40:52.810
He’s not attached to anything but He can
take away everything that you think is sin,

40:52.810 --> 40:57.799
because He’s sinless, He so pure, immaculate.

40:57.799 --> 41:01.539
All right does that give you some hopes?

41:01.539 --> 41:06.190
Or still you are indulging into your own miseries?

41:06.190 --> 41:10.519
Question: Can You give us some guide about
diet.

41:10.519 --> 41:11.969
Shri Mataji: Diet?

41:11.969 --> 41:12.969
All right.

41:12.969 --> 41:17.349
