head.

01:19:53.970 --> 01:20:00.130
It is the vibrations when they are flowing
that’s the best stage, when you have pierced

01:20:00.130 --> 01:20:01.630
through your Bramarundra.

01:20:01.630 --> 01:20:06.510
So the second stage starts from Nirvikalpa
Samadhi growing into, which many of the Sahaja

01:20:06.510 --> 01:20:14.750
Yogis have achieved in Australia, is called
as Nirvikalpa, where the is no doubts.

01:20:14.750 --> 01:20:18.060
You have no doubts left about Sahaja Yoga,
you have no doubts left about yourself.

01:20:18.060 --> 01:20:23.550
It’s a state, it’s not that by mentally
or rationally but it’s a state.

01:20:23.550 --> 01:20:28.220
Where you see it so clearly, white is white,
you don’t have to doubt that whether my

01:20:28.220 --> 01:20:30.680
eyes are showing white or black, you see.

01:20:30.680 --> 01:20:35.640
That state is reached is called as Nirvikalpa
where the no vikalpa, you just go, move steadily

01:20:35.640 --> 01:20:40.470
and that’s the best stage where you really
grow faster because you’re so steady and

01:20:40.470 --> 01:20:42.080
that stage must be achieved.

01:20:42.080 --> 01:20:46.650
So try to achieve that stage through negating
things, “Nethi, nethi, vachinay nigamoor,”

01:20:46.650 --> 01:20:54.630
by saying, “Not this, not this, not this,”
and you reach that stage, is very clearly

01:20:54.630 --> 01:20:55.630
given.

01:20:55.630 --> 01:21:02.940
You see the trouble is, so many of these books
which are so great are never translated, people

01:21:02.940 --> 01:21:03.940
do not know about them.

01:21:03.940 --> 01:21:09.270
Now after coming to Sahaja Yoga you will be
exposed to them and you will see what truths

01:21:09.270 --> 01:21:22.130
there are and how Sahaja Yoga verifies it
and proves it.

01:21:22.130 --> 01:21:26.500
Question: What influence are you likely to
have on those around him or on people who

01:21:26.500 --> 01:21:29.540
live with You who are not realised.

01:21:29.540 --> 01:21:36.790
What is the realised souls influence in that
type of environment?

01:21:36.790 --> 01:21:45.830
Shri Mataji:You see if you have stones and
if you have living trees, stones do not receive

01:21:45.830 --> 01:21:51.840
anything from the sun but the leaves receive
something isn’t it, they are more sensitive,

01:21:51.840 --> 01:21:53.190
that’s the difference.

01:21:53.190 --> 01:21:58.790
Then in Sahaja yoga there’s a possibility
that you can convert stones into living beings,

01:21:58.790 --> 01:22:00.630
can be done.

01:22:00.630 --> 01:22:10.550
Yes, because they see, you see they see you,
they understand the value that you are, gradually,

01:22:10.550 --> 01:22:16.330
rationally they start understanding then they
reach certain conclusions, then they come

01:22:16.330 --> 01:22:20.540
to Sahaja Yog, then they get realised, it
works out that way.

01:22:20.540 --> 01:22:24.450
But with seekers it’s very different, seekers
just jump into it.

01:22:24.450 --> 01:22:26.980
They do not think about it they just get it.

01:22:26.980 --> 01:22:31.560
They get it so fast that they don’t think
about it, they just they get it.

01:22:31.560 --> 01:22:39.140
So they are so sensitive that’s the difference.

01:22:39.140 --> 01:22:49.550
Question: Can we help our loved ones who do
not want to listen to anything particularly

01:22:49.550 --> 01:22:51.220
about Sahaja Yoga?

01:22:51.220 --> 01:22:56.960
Shri Mataji: You see there’s nobody else
that you help someone, they are all within

01:22:56.960 --> 01:22:57.960
yourself.

01:22:57.960 --> 01:23:02.810
On the contrary, I would say better to have
them together who are Sahaja yogis because

01:23:02.810 --> 01:23:06.910
those who are not will trouble you, it will
be a problem, leave them alone, they’ll

01:23:06.910 --> 01:23:08.540
be all right, they’ll come round.

01:23:08.540 --> 01:23:13.650
Let them come on their own you cannot force
them, they’re loved ones, you’ll change

01:23:13.650 --> 01:23:18.940
now your priorities, you’ll understand that
those who are really loved ones are not really

01:23:18.940 --> 01:23:21.100
your brothers and sisters.

01:23:21.100 --> 01:23:28.500
As Christ has said, “Who are my brothers
and sisters?” Now we have to ask that question.

01:23:28.500 --> 01:23:32.380
Because you speak another language, you are
a different person, not that you give them

01:23:32.380 --> 01:23:34.360
up, but they exist.

01:23:34.360 --> 01:23:37.870
But they haven’t got your awareness so is
a different thing all together.

01:23:37.870 --> 01:23:43.840
But you help them in a way, gradually they
see you but if you force them they’ll run

01:23:43.840 --> 01:23:44.840
away.

01:23:44.840 --> 01:23:48.970
No use forcing or telling them anything about
it but you show your satisfaction and happiness

01:23:48.970 --> 01:23:54.640
and your growth and others get impressed by
it and they just come to you.

01:23:54.640 --> 01:23:59.970
Question: how can you..Do You help them?

01:23:59.970 --> 01:24:02.750
Shri Mataji: Yes, I do.

01:24:02.750 --> 01:24:06.290
But you should put them out of your minds
and say, “Mother, You help.

01:24:06.290 --> 01:24:20.560
If You try to help, then I’ll leave it to
You."

01:24:20.560 --> 01:24:26.020
Question: He cannot understand why You say
that Christ died for us.

