01:25:07.290 --> 01:25:08.410
You represent them.

01:25:08.410 --> 01:25:14.000
When you are realised then you are different
people, then you are resurrected.

01:25:14.000 --> 01:25:19.600
His message was resurrection not crucifixion
but that shows the stupidity of these people,

01:25:19.600 --> 01:25:20.600
isn’t it.

01:25:20.600 --> 01:25:41.270
I mean you may do that again I can’t say,
there are people.

01:25:41.270 --> 01:26:02.340
Question: Is it possible to exercise love
