01:28:08.550 --> 01:28:13.780
You see you have all of you, you see have
developed a philosophy where you say that

01:28:13.780 --> 01:28:17.340
nobody is evil, everything is fine.

01:28:17.340 --> 01:28:22.570
This is a very good philosophy to work with
because you also fit into the thing.

