01:29:02.200 --> 01:29:05.450
you, I see them very clearly and I have to
tell you.

01:29:05.450 --> 01:29:12.000
So love doesn’t mean that I love a snake,
will you go and love a snake, a snake must

01:29:12.000 --> 01:29:16.429
understand first of all.

01:29:16.429 --> 01:29:20.500
In the same way we have to understand there
are evil people, that’s true.

01:29:20.500 --> 01:29:26.080
That is what is very much in the West, I see,
“Oh, you love everyone is all right.

01:29:26.080 --> 01:29:28.700
But you don’t love a snake, do you?

01:29:28.700 --> 01:29:31.350
Go and have, ask snake, “I want to love
