01:29:44.730 --> 01:29:50.400
You don’t know what I have to go through,
such a lot of work to cure you when you are

01:29:50.400 --> 01:29:51.500
affected by these people.

01:29:51.500 --> 01:29:55.260
You don’t know how much I’ve worked, morning
till evening.

01:29:55.260 --> 01:30:02.000
This morning I started six o’clock till
I came here just ten minutes I got to change

01:30:02.000 --> 01:30:04.200
My sari and I was here.

01:30:04.200 --> 01:30:08.600
These are affected by other gurus and things
and I have to take it out.

01:30:08.600 --> 01:30:10.120
I know what harm they have done to you.

01:30:10.120 --> 01:30:16.110
You have no idea.

01:30:16.110 --> 01:30:25.050
Question: What are Your objections to chanting
and singing the holy scriptures?

01:30:25.050 --> 01:30:33.720
Shri Mataji: Not at all, who told you I am,
I’m not but you must understand that without

01:30:33.720 --> 01:30:38.030
understanding what chanting is needed it’s
like a medicine.

01:30:38.030 --> 01:30:40.510
Chanting is a mantra.

01:30:40.510 --> 01:30:52.550
Mantra means a thing that acts as a sound
to correct a particular thing within you,

01:30:52.550 --> 01:30:53.590
all right.

01:30:53.590 --> 01:30:57.220
It’s you can say sound therapy it is, all
right.

01:30:57.220 --> 01:31:03.260
Now you have to know what medicine is needed
for which charka, also you must know where

01:31:03.260 --> 01:31:07.710
is the problem with you, or with anybody else.

01:31:07.710 --> 01:31:13.380
I mean it would be chanting at random means
sometimes it would be sort of an indiscriminate

01:31:13.380 --> 01:31:16.150
drinking of all the medicines, you see.

01:31:16.150 --> 01:31:20.380
Taking all the medicines bottles into your
stomach emptying them without understanding.

01:31:20.380 --> 01:31:25.290
We do chant but we know where to chant, what.

01:31:25.290 --> 01:31:27.750
You see, not indiscriminate, just like that.

01:31:27.750 --> 01:31:33.350
And it’s very dangerous because when you
go on chanting say, Rama’s name or Krishna’s

01:31:33.350 --> 01:31:34.350
name.

01:31:34.350 --> 01:31:38.400
Now when you say Krishna’s name, Krishna
is here, if your Kundalini has not reached

01:31:38.400 --> 01:31:44.220
there up to this point if you take Krishna’s
name it’s very, very annoying for Krishna

01:31:44.220 --> 01:31:46.970
Himself and He recedes, sleeps off.

01:31:46.970 --> 01:31:53.260
He freezes sometimes and by that you develop
problems of the chakras and sometimes you

01:31:53.260 --> 01:31:57.630
develop throat cancer, it’s very serious.

01:31:57.630 --> 01:32:03.810
So first, you must know where is your Kundalini,
where it has gone, where it has stopped.

01:32:03.810 --> 01:32:08.200
Then you should know what is the problem,
then you must know what exactly is the chanting

01:32:08.200 --> 01:32:11.350
to be used, all right, and then cure that
part.

01:32:11.350 --> 01:32:17.800
You see so it’s a big science, which has
to be understood in Sahaja Yoga, it’s not

01:32:17.800 --> 01:32:18.800
at random.

01:32:18.800 --> 01:32:24.570
You are suffering from whatever trouble you
are suffering from, you must know first of

01:32:24.570 --> 01:32:25.570
all.

01:32:25.570 --> 01:32:30.620
See many people who are Christians catch on
Agnya I told you, they do, because it’s

01:32:30.620 --> 01:32:31.620
unauthorised.

01:32:31.620 --> 01:32:39.790
Christ, we treat Him as if I don’t know
what, some passion fruit hanging in a tree.

01:32:39.790 --> 01:32:43.170
Do we know who He is?

01:32:43.170 --> 01:32:46.560
There is a protocol, great protocol.

01:32:46.560 --> 01:32:50.910
Even Brahma, Vishnu Mahesh could not reach
Him.

01:32:50.910 --> 01:32:57.910
So for us because we think we are born among
Christian families and because the church

01:32:57.910 --> 01:33:03.660
