It’s very dangerous for your children also,
so many children have died with this kind

01:34:36.130 --> 01:34:37.130
of a thing.

01:34:37.130 --> 01:34:43.110
I mean you develop especially cancer, this
multiple scleroses or anything like that.

01:34:43.110 --> 01:34:45.840
All these come from spiritualists.

01:34:45.840 --> 01:34:50.750
These are all spiritualists, these gurus are
